WEBVTT

00:01.935 --> 00:03.562
<i>Previously on</i> One Tree Hill:

00:03.636 --> 00:05.035
-Take off the wedding ring.
-What?

00:05.105 --> 00:07.665
-Let them think you're a couple.
-But we're not a couple.

00:07.741 --> 00:09.003
<i>Are you a couple in real life?</i>

00:09.075 --> 00:10.975
<i>-Actually--</i>
<i>-You know, the music never lies.</i>

00:11.044 --> 00:13.069
Somebody bashed in
my car windshield last night.

00:13.146 --> 00:15.239
I mean, could things get any worse?

00:17.917 --> 00:19.282
You wanna ask me that again?

00:19.352 --> 00:21.320
I fell in love with Keith for real.

00:21.388 --> 00:23.413
I want him to know who you really are.

00:24.691 --> 00:27.159
I'm sorry. She left.

00:30.730 --> 00:31.890
I didn't do anything.

00:31.965 --> 00:33.762
You sick bastard.

00:34.034 --> 00:36.628
I found out about your arrangement
and I went to Jules.

00:36.703 --> 00:38.694
And I threatened to tell the truth.

00:38.772 --> 00:40.171
My dad got that job...

00:40.240 --> 00:41.571
in California.

00:41.641 --> 00:43.541
We're moving next week.

00:43.610 --> 00:45.077
What are we gonna do?

00:45.145 --> 00:46.578
<i>I don't want to go.</i>

00:53.253 --> 00:54.379
What are you doing here?

00:54.454 --> 00:56.445
Go get Haley. She's your wife.

